            <h1>About SlackToSurplus</h1>
            <p class="project-description">
                <strong>Project Name:</strong> SlackToSurplus<br>
                <strong>Problem Statement:</strong> <em>JFSD-PS09: Reduce food wastage and improve food security</em>
            </p>
            <p class="mission">
                SlackToSurplus is a platform dedicated to reducing food wastage and enhancing food security. 
                Our goal is to track and minimize food waste, offering resources for effective food management,
                raising awareness on food waste impacts, and improving the equitable distribution of food resources.
            </p>
            
            <h2>Our Solution</h2>
            <p class="solution">
                Our app provides tools to manage food resources, educate on food waste consequences, and support those in need. 
                By connecting food donors and recipient organizations, we create a seamless pathway for redistributing surplus food 
                to communities, aiming to build a sustainable solution for food security.
            </p>

            <h2>Key Roles on the Platform</h2>
            <ul class="roles">
                <li><strong>Admin:</strong> Oversees platform content, manages user interactions, and ensures data accuracy.</li>
                <li><strong>Food Donor:</strong> Lists surplus food, coordinates donations, and tracks the positive impact of their contributions.</li>
                <li><strong>Recipient Organization:</strong> Requests food donations, manages logistics, and distributes resources to those in need.</li>
                <li><strong>Data Analyst:</strong> Tracks food waste trends, analyzes data, and generates reports to drive efficiency and reduce waste.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
